<script>
import BlogPost from '../components/testBlog'
  
export default {
  components: {
    BlogPost
  },
  data() {
    return {
      posts: [
        { id: 1, title: 'My journey with Vue' },
        { id: 2, title: 'Blogging with Vue' },
        { id: 3, title: 'Why Vue is so fun' }
      ]
    }
  }
}
</script>

<template>
	<BlogPost
  	v-for="post in posts"
	  :key="post.id"
  	:title="post.title"
	></BlogPost>
</template>
